These are instructions for setting up the deposit application as a developer:

0. install setuptools http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools
1. easy_install django
2. easy_install twill
3. easy_install pysqlite
4. svn co https://rdc.lctl.gov/svn/transfer/deposit/trunk deposit
5. cp deposit/conf/dev-settings.py deposit/deposit/settings.py
6. cd deposit/deposit
7. python manage.py syncdb
8. python manage.py test
9. python manage.py runserver
